and think of the difference at two points, <i>f</i>[<i>x</i> + <i>h</i>] and <i>f</i>[<i>x</i>]—
并思考两个点的区别 <i>f</i>[<i>x</i>+<i>h</i>] 和 <i>f</i>[<i>x</i>]

