00:03:44,000 --> 00:03:47,000
Now that difference over here would just be
现在 这里的差异将只是

56
00:03:47,000 --> 00:03:52,000
the area of a tiny strip because <i>h</i> is very small.
因为 <i>h</i> 非常小 所以是一个小带子的面积

