00:04:05,000 --> 00:04:11,000
But then that is <i>f</i>[<i>x</i> + <i>h</i>] – <i>f</i>[<i>x</i>], so if you divide,
但那就是 <i>f</i>[<i>x</i>+<i>h</i>]-<i>f</i>[<i>x</i>] 所以如果你做除法

61
00:04:11,000 --> 00:04:13,000
then you get back this relation over here.
然后你回顾这个关系

